between their parents 
whenever they see a lot of clouds and whenever they see a lot 
of wind they get scared mrs mendoza said adding that her 
seven children dont range about town as far as they used to and 
are more quick to go inside when it becomes windy and rainy 
mrs candelas said she misses the nightly soccer games children 
used to play near her house 
i used to get mad because they made so much noise she said 
they used to come out at night now theyre afraid theyre 
afraid if they come the tornado will get them here 
