those of a white house aspirant 
fortunately i have been able to combine the two fairly well 
all things considered he said recently i think i can probably 
continue to do that certainly i am going to work hard at doing 
that 
but critics question how effectively hes handled the dual role 
they point to delays in enacting a 3 billion transportation bond 
in january and in dealing with recently discovered multimillion 
