brain doctors repaired the second aneurysm during a 4 12 hour 
operation on may 3 
an aneurysm is a weakened area in an artery the pressure of 
blood causes the area to balloon forming a blisterlike flaw on 
the side of the artery 
to correct the problem doctors perform microscopic surgery 
inserting a metal clip into the head that locks at the base of the 
flaw the clip remains in the head 
further complicating bidens recovery was a blood clot that 
doctors found in his lung on march 13 the clot was absorbed into 
the body without any damage but to prevent further problems 
doctors inserted a tiny filter into a major vein to prevent other 
clots from reaching the lungs 
biden said he never feared for his life despite the severity of 
the operations particularly the first one in which he said doctors 
told him his changes of surviving were a little better than 
even 
