president reagan leaves this week for a summit 
in moscow that under a diplomatic code of reciprocity will be 
amazingly similar to soviet leader mikhail gorbachevs visit in 
washington late last year 
begin with their cars gorbachev shipped his zil limousine to 
washington instead of relying on his host for transportation so 
reagan will follow suit sending his armored cadillac to moscow 
